<L>__{interior kitchen, ron's house night}
<A>__{as chris enters, ron is pulling the steaks from the broiler. above the kitchen sink, chris sees a row of approximately ten photographs, each in vertical 4x6 frames, some black and white, some color: all of japanese boys and girls in formal american and japanese attire.}
